Engineering Animation names financial officer . Engineering Animation Inc said Monday that Jerome Behar has been named vice president of finance and chief financial officerBehar succeeds Michael Jewell , who is leaving EAI to manage a family business in Seattle . In another development , Adrian Sannier has been promoted to vice president and general manager of EAI ' s interactive and custom animation business units , a new position . EAI provides 3D visualization technology for education and entertainment needs . ( ( Chicago newsdesk 312 408 8787 ) ) 
